'''Otolia Ratiuv''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Noolan]] [[Technician/Legends|technician]]. Her body was taken over by [[Nana]] when an explosion caused Nana's body to be badly damaged. It was thanks to a [[Force crystal|Jedi Force Crystal]] that this transference was possible.

